00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:26,640
Ya, ya.

387
00:31:28,039 --> 00:31:30,079
Kapan lorinya tiba?
Mobil harus dipindahkan.

388
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:33,640
Sudah setengah jam aku di sini.

389
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:35,240
- DCI Sharma.
- Baik, Pak.

390
00:31:37,119 --> 00:31:38,079
- Sampai nanti.
- Dah.

391
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:41,759
Hei, Bos.

392
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:44,240
Kendaraan dilaporkan mencurigakan,

393
