394
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,920
Nama pelanggan Adrian Smith.

395
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:52,400
Sama dengan nama di Rumah Pascoe.

396
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:56,799
