dan tak ada ANPR terpicu.

397
00:31:58,519 --> 00:32:00,839
Hubungi perusahaan sewa.
Kita akan tahu siapa dia.

398
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:01,839
Baik, Pak.

399
00:32:11,160 --> 00:32:12,039
PS Budd.

400
00:32:12,359 --> 00:32:14,759
