00:43:12,119 --> 00:43:13,840
Terima kasih menyambutku di sini.

505
00:43:15,079 --> 00:43:16,599
Julia Montague. Apa kabar?

506
00:43:17,280 --> 00:43:18,880
- Gerakan terbaik, Bu.
- Julia.

507
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:20,679
- Senang bertemu.
- Ke sini, Mendagri.

508
00:43:22,760 --> 00:43:24,480
Aku bicara sebentar dengan asistenku.

509
00:43:24,679 --> 00:43:25,679
- Ya.
- Terima kasih.

510
00:43:31,039 --> 00:43:32,400
